id3shit - Less sucky id3-editor

All ID3-editors that I've tried sucked. This suck too, but not as much.

  USAGE: id3shit.pl [OPTIONS] <FILES>

  OPTIONS:
    -t  --tags    Show ID3V{1,2} tags
    -i  --info    Show audio information
    -r  --remove  Remove known tags
    -w  --write   Write tags. The syntax is --write FIELD VALUE FILE
                  Legal fields are ARTIST, ALBUM, TITLE, YEAR, COMMENT,
                  TRACKNUM, GENRE.

                  Examples:
                  --write artist laleh *.mp3
                  Will give us something like:
                  >> ARTIST: Laleh

###############################################################################

To install dependencies:
  # cpan MP3::Info;
To install id3shit, just move it to /usr/local/bin or anywhere in your $PATH.
